    "title": "service-xapi-services",
    "description": "## API Overview\n\n**Architecture Layer:** Experience Layer (XAPI) - Part of ETB's API-led connectivity architecture\n\n**Service Name:** service-xapi-services\n**Total Operations:** 1\n**Documentation Quality:** 60% RAML Coverage\n\n## Core Capabilities\n\n# Service Experience API Services\n\n## Standards Compliance\n\n- OpenAPI 3.0.3 Specification\n- ETB API Design Guidelines\n- OAuth 2.0 Security Standards\n- RESTful API Design Principles\n- TM Forum Open APIs Compliance\n\n## Mock Server Information\n\nThis specification includes mock examples for all operations to facilitate API testing and integration development without requiring live backend connectivity.",
